<figureCitation id="131A2A147E36FFC5982CFCF1FE272415" box="[306,387,836,860]" captionStart="FIGURES 12 – 15" captionStartId="4.[151,264,1474,1497]" captionTargetBox="[151,1428,193,1427]" captionTargetId="figure@4.[151,1436,193,1453]" captionTargetPageId="4" captionText="FIGURES 12 – 15. Simulium (I.) littopyga n. sp. (12). Hypogynial valves. Scale bar = 0.1 mm. (13). Spermatheca. Scale bar = 0.02 mm. (14). Genital fork. Scale bar = 0.05 mm. (15). Cercus &amp; anal lobe. Scale bar = 0.05 mm." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/847900/files/figure.png" pageId="5" pageNumber="378">FIg. 13</figureCitation>
