<figureCitation id="131A2A147E36FFC59A6DFCF0FC132415" box="[883,951,836,861]" captionStart="FIGURES 1 – 6" captionStartId="2.[151,264,1933,1956]" captionTargetBox="[196,1400,235,1921]" captionTargetId="figure@2.[196,1400,193,1921]" captionTargetPageId="2" captionText="FIGURES 1 – 6. Simulium (I) littopyga n. sp. (1). Holotype, female Simulium (I.) littopyga. In ETOH. Scale bar = 0.5 mm. (2) Frontal view of head. Scale bar = 0.2 mm. (3). Antenna. Scale bar = 0.1 mm. (4). Maxillary palp, mandible, lacinia. Scale bar = 0.1 mm. (5). Mandible apex. Scale bar = 0.02 mm. (6). Cibarium. Scale bar = 0.05 mm." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/847896/files/figure.png" pageId="5" pageNumber="378">FIg. 4</figureCitation>
